12:52.005 --> 12:53.473
I GET IT.

12:53.507 --> 12:56.543
IF I GOT SHOT IN MY JERK‐OFF
ARM, I WOULD BE MAD, TOO.

12:58.612 --> 13:00.581
I'M NOT MAD.

13:00.614 --> 13:03.150
HOW MANY PILLS
DID YOU TAKE?

13:04.751 --> 13:05.853
NONE.

13:05.886 --> 13:08.355
WELL, THAT'S DUMB.

13:08.388 --> 13:09.890
I'LL GET YOU
A GLASS OF WATER.

13:09.923 --> 13:11.325
HEY, GIVE ME YOUR PILLS.
I'LL OPEN THEM.

13:11.358 --> 13:12.960
NO.

13:12.993 --> 13:15.128
WHY HAVE THEM
IF YOU WON'T TAKE THEM?

13:15.162 --> 13:19.066
BECAUSE...
THEY'RE MINE.

13:26.540 --> 13:28.976
I LIKE
THE WAY IT FEELS.

13:29.009 --> 13:33.981
LIKE A KNIFE POPPING
THE SAME BALLOON OVER AND OVER,

13:34.014 --> 13:36.450
ONLY YOU DON'T HAVE TO
BLOW UP A NEW ONE.

13:36.483 --> 13:40.721
I CAN MAKE THE PAIN GO AWAY
ANYTIME WITH A PILL,

13:40.754 --> 13:44.224
BUT I DON'T WANT TO.

13:44.258 --> 13:48.595
I DON'T HAVE TO THINK
ABOUT ANYTHING ELSE.

13:48.629 --> 13:50.764
IT'S GREAT.

13:53.534 --> 13:56.303
YEAH...

13:56.336 --> 13:58.172
GREAT.

14:12.419 --> 14:14.721
[ GRUNTS ]

14:14.755 --> 14:17.824
WELL...
THAT'S THE LAST OF IT.

14:17.858 --> 14:19.126
[ BREATHING HEAVILY ]

14:19.159 --> 14:20.928
WHO KNEW YOU HAD
SO MUCH STUFF?

14:20.961 --> 14:22.796
THANK YOU FOR HELPING ME
MOVE IN, DEAN.

14:22.829 --> 14:24.932
I REALLY APPRECIATE IT.

14:24.965 --> 14:27.601
WHAT'S 12 FLIGHTS OF STAIRS
BETWEEN PARTNERS?

14:27.634 --> 14:31.471
EXACTLY. AND WE COULD NOT
RISK USING THE ELEVATOR.

14:31.505 --> 14:33.507
THERE'S AN ELEVATOR?

14:33.540 --> 14:36.844
WHERE DID THOSE IDIOTS
GET ALL THIS POT, ANYHOW?

14:36.877 --> 14:39.179
SOME GUY
NAMED "THE WIZARD."

14:39.213 --> 14:42.716
WHOA. CHECK IT OUT.

14:42.749 --> 14:45.018
FOUR DEAD BOLTS.

14:45.052 --> 14:47.721
STEEL‐REINFORCED HINGES.

14:47.754 --> 14:49.523
CODED ENTRY SYSTEM!

14:49.556 --> 14:52.059
YOU'VE REALLY GOT THIS PLACE
LOCKED DOWN.

14:52.092 --> 14:54.962
PLUS, THERE'S
A SECURITY GUARD DOWNSTAIRS,

14:54.995 --> 14:57.231
AND CHANNEL 3
ON THE TELEVISION

14:57.264 --> 15:00.901
PICKS UP A LIVE FEED
OF THE FRONT GATE.

15:00.934 --> 15:04.271
I AM PROTECTING
OUR INVESTMENT.

15:04.304 --> 15:05.806
YOU ARE SCARY‐GOOD
AT THIS.

15:05.839 --> 15:09.276
THANK YOU. I KNOW.

15:09.309 --> 15:10.978
WHAT IF I NEED TO GET IN?

15:12.212 --> 15:15.849
MAYBE YOU NEED
A SECRET KNOCK.

15:15.883 --> 15:18.552
REALLY?

15:18.585 --> 15:19.786
COOL. LIKE WHAT?

15:19.820 --> 15:21.288
I DON'T KNOW.

15:21.321 --> 15:23.857
MAYBE YOU SHOULD
MAKE ONE UP.

15:23.891 --> 15:26.693
OKAY.
UM, OH, I GOT ONE.

15:26.727 --> 15:28.061
[ LOCK TURNS ]

15:29.229 --> 15:32.566
[ RHYTHMIC KNOCKING ON DOOR ]

15:32.599 --> 15:34.535
Dean: HOW'S THAT?

15:34.568 --> 15:35.869
CELIA?

15:35.903 --> 15:39.840
SECURITY, THERE'S A SWEATY JEW
IN MY HALLWAY.

15:39.873 --> 15:42.943
[ KNOCKING CONTINUES ]

15:42.976 --> 15:45.779
HOW MUCH?
A LOT OF MONEY.

15:45.812 --> 15:47.281
IT'LL BE YOUR
BANK ACCOUNT.

15:47.314 --> 15:50.384
YOU CAN ACCESS IT WITH
AN ATM CARD FROM ANY COUNTRY.

15:50.417 --> 15:51.818
ALSO ‐‐
MOM ‐‐

15:51.852 --> 15:53.487
PICK A PLACE,
SOMEWHERE FAR.

15:53.520 --> 15:55.489
ARE YOU SERIOUS?
EUROPE. GO TO EUROPE.

15:55.522 --> 15:57.658
WESTERN EUROPE.
THE FOOD'S BETTER.

15:57.691 --> 15:59.259
AMSTERDAM?

15:59.293 --> 16:02.996
SURE, AMSTERDAM. START THERE.
I'LL GET YOU A EURO PASS.

16:03.030 --> 16:05.666
YOU CAN GO TO MUSEUMS,
STAY IN HOSTELS,

16:05.699 --> 16:07.568
SEDUCE TRAVELING
AUSTRALIANS.

16:07.601 --> 16:09.403
WHAT'S THE CATCH?

16:09.436 --> 16:10.537
THERE IS NO CATCH.

16:10.571 --> 16:12.573
THIS IS WHAT YOU DO
WHEN YOU'RE YOUNG.

16:12.606 --> 16:14.441
YOU TRAVEL THROUGH EUROPE
WITH A BACKPACK.

16:14.474 --> 16:16.844
SOMEONE IN THIS FAMILY SHOULD
BE DOING SOMETHING NORMAL.

16:16.877 --> 16:18.412
WHY NOT YOU?

16:20.547 --> 16:22.482
[ SIGHS ]

16:22.516 --> 16:26.720
I HAVE BEEN REPLACED
AS CANDIDATE FOR GOVERNOR.

16:28.655 --> 16:30.624
[ SIGHS ]

16:30.657 --> 16:32.426
YOU LEAVE TOMORROW.

16:35.829 --> 16:37.865
IT WAS CELIA!
SHE FORCED ME TO LIE!

16:37.898 --> 16:39.166
I DIDN'T WANT TO DO IT.

16:39.199 --> 16:42.269
UH‐HUH, AND WHAT DID
SHE PROMISE YOU? SEX? MONEY.

16:42.302 --> 16:43.704
NO, SHE ‐‐

16:43.737 --> 16:45.639
COME TO THINK OF IT,
SHE NEVER PROMISED ME ANYTHING.

16:45.672 --> 16:48.876
BETRAYER. COCK‐BREAKER.
HOW COULD YOU DO THIS?

16:48.909 --> 16:49.810
I DIDN'T HAVE A CHOICE.

16:49.843 --> 16:51.144
I AM BELLY‐UP, BUDDY.

16:51.178 --> 16:53.881
YOU PUT A KEY ON MY KITE
IN A SHITSTORM.

16:53.914 --> 16:55.849
I DROPPED 5 GRAND
ON LIP LINER!

16:55.883 --> 16:57.050
YOU TOOK AWAY MY BUSINESS!

16:57.084 --> 16:58.785
MY SPLOOGE DOESN'T
WANT TO COME OUT!

16:58.819 --> 17:00.888
IT'S STUCK IN A POCKET
BETWEEN MY BALLS!

17:00.921 --> 17:02.422
WELL, HOW DO YOU THINK
I FEEL, HUH?

17:02.456 --> 17:03.590
SHE SQUEEZED ME OUT!

17:03.624 --> 17:06.927
I WAS GONNA BE A DRUG KINGPIN.
I WAS GONNA BE TONY MONTANA.

17:06.960 --> 17:08.095
I GOT NOTHING!

17:08.128 --> 17:11.131
WHAT'S WITH ALL
THE MOVING BOXES?

17:11.164 --> 17:12.799
I GOT TO GIVE UP THE SPACE.
I CAN'T AFFORD TO KEEP IT.

17:12.833 --> 17:14.301
THIS A FRESH POT?

17:14.334 --> 17:15.769
YEAH.

17:15.802 --> 17:17.104
SHE LOOTED ME, BUDDY.

17:17.137 --> 17:18.505
WANT TO CALL THE FEDS?

17:18.539 --> 17:19.640
I'D BE DISBARRED.

17:19.673 --> 17:21.642
I'D BE FINE.

17:21.675 --> 17:23.043
HEY,
WE'RE IN THIS TOGETHER.

17:23.076 --> 17:24.278
NOT UNTIL WE'RE EVEN.

17:24.311 --> 17:25.646
EVEN?

17:25.679 --> 17:28.015
YEAH. TEENY DEANY.

17:28.882 --> 17:30.884
DIP 'EM IN.
WHAT?

17:30.918 --> 17:32.586
WHIP 'EM OUT.
DIP 'EM IN.

17:32.619 --> 17:34.721
ARE YOU OUT OF YOUR
FUCKING MIND? GET AWAY
FROM ME WITH THAT.

17:34.755 --> 17:38.091
YOU WANT TO GO UP AGAINST CELIA?
YOU'RE GONNA NEED MY HELP.

17:38.125 --> 17:41.161
DROP THE PANTS.
DUNK THE DEAN NUTS.

17:41.195 --> 17:43.130
MY BAL‐‐
NO, NOT MY BALLS.

17:43.163 --> 17:44.431
YES, BALLS, AND I SEE YOU
TRYING TO GET HARD.

17:44.464 --> 17:47.334
UNH‐UNH. NO WAY.
FLACCID IN THE ACID.

17:47.367 --> 17:49.069
BUT ‐‐
DUNK!

17:55.542 --> 17:58.545
[ UNZIPS ]

18:02.015 --> 18:04.985
[ DEAN SCREAMING ]

18:11.091 --> 18:12.893
YOU HAVE THE VOTES.

18:12.926 --> 18:15.229
WHY AREN'T YOU FIGHTING?
YOU COULD WIN.

18:15.262 --> 18:19.433
I DON'T KNOW.
PILAR HAS AN ARMY.

18:19.466 --> 18:20.834
YOU HAVE THE PEOPLE.

18:20.868 --> 18:22.970
IN AMERICA, WE CALL IT
"WAGGING THE DOG."

18:23.003 --> 18:24.471
[ CHUCKLES ]

18:24.505 --> 18:27.207
WELL, IN MY COUNTRY,
DOGS TRAVEL IN PACKS.

18:27.241 --> 18:28.809
SO, THAT'S IT? SHE WINS?

18:28.842 --> 18:31.979
YEAH. SHE WON.

18:32.012 --> 18:34.147
NOW WE CAN BE MARRIED

18:34.181 --> 18:37.351
AND HAVE A BEAUTIFUL,
LAVISH WEDDING

18:37.384 --> 18:39.987
WITH ALL OUR FRIENDS
AND FAMILY.

18:40.020 --> 18:43.023
AND I WILL FEED YOU CAKE.

18:44.424 --> 18:48.061
SMALL CEREMONY, NO FRIENDS,
LIMITED FAMILY.

18:48.095 --> 18:50.130
CHOCOLATE CAKE.
ENTENMANN'S.

18:51.532 --> 18:54.501
I CANNOT PUT YOU AND YOUR FAMILY
IN ANY MORE DANGER.

18:54.535 --> 18:56.803
SO YOU WOULD RUN
IF IT WASN'T FOR ME,

18:56.837 --> 18:58.672
IF YOU DIDN'T
HAVE A FAMILY?

18:58.705 --> 19:00.674
I DID NOT SAY THAT.

19:02.075 --> 19:03.744
AND YOU WOULD WIN.

19:03.777 --> 19:07.814
YES. I WOULD WIN.

19:07.848 --> 19:09.583
THEN DO IT.

19:21.061 --> 19:23.864
SO, I GAVE IT SOME THOUGHT,

19:23.897 --> 19:27.868
AND I RESPECTFULLY...

19:27.901 --> 19:29.169
DECLINE YOUR OFFER.

19:29.203 --> 19:31.605
NO, YOU'RE NOT DECLINING.
NO.

19:31.638 --> 19:32.406
I'M NOT GOING.

19:32.439 --> 19:34.708
THIS IS NOT
UP FOR DISCUSSION.

19:34.741 --> 19:38.045
ESTEBAN'S DECIDED TO RUN
FOR GOVERNOR INDEPENDENTLY.

19:38.078 --> 19:40.447
I'LL BE SURE AND WEAR
HIS CAMPAIGN T‐SHIRT.

19:40.480 --> 19:44.952
WHICH MEANS YOU NOT HERE,
WHICH MEANS ONE SON LESS

19:44.985 --> 19:47.287
TO KEEP TRACK OF,
TO WORRY ABOUT.

19:47.321 --> 19:49.122
SHANE'S HERE.
STEVIE'S HERE.

19:49.156 --> 19:51.658
THEY'RE KIDS. YOU'RE OLD ENOUGH
TO TAKE CARE OF YOURSELF.

19:51.692 --> 19:53.126
YOUR BROTHERS
WILL BE FINE.

19:53.160 --> 19:55.229
[ SHANE BELCHES ]

19:56.496 --> 19:57.631
SAY "EXCUSE ME."

19:57.664 --> 19:58.765
NO.

19:58.799 --> 20:00.434
I'M ANNOUNCING
IN A WEEK.

20:00.467 --> 20:02.536
YOU SHOULD BE GONE
BEFORE THEN.

20:02.569 --> 20:03.504
LISTEN TO HIM.

20:03.537 --> 20:05.873
UH, I APPRECIATE
YOU BEING PREEMPTIVE,

20:05.906 --> 20:07.040
FOR ONCE IN OUR LIVES,
BUT ‐‐

20:07.074 --> 20:09.276
HOW IS IT THAT I HAVE TO
BEG AN 18‐YEAR‐OLD

20:09.309 --> 20:12.045
TO TRAVEL EUROPE WITH A WAD
OF CASH AND MY BLESSING?

20:12.079 --> 20:15.048
HOW IS IT THAT
YOU EXPECT ME TO BELIEVE

20:15.082 --> 20:16.750
THAT MY BROTHERS
WILL BE FINE?

20:16.783 --> 20:19.219
NO ONE IS FINE
AROUND YOU.

20:19.253 --> 20:23.423
SO [SCOFFS] I'M STAYING.

20:23.457 --> 20:25.859
HERE. IN THIS HOUSE.

20:25.893 --> 20:30.731
THIS BEER'S WARM!
SOMEONE GET ME ANOTHER!

20:30.764 --> 20:32.032
WHERE'S
THE FUCKING STAFF?

20:32.065 --> 20:33.567
I HAVE THIRST!

20:33.600 --> 20:35.068
NO MORE BEER!

20:35.102 --> 20:39.106
AND YOU BETTER PROTECT US.

20:40.474 --> 20:42.776
I CAN DO THAT.

20:42.809 --> 20:45.445
HE CAN DO THAT.

20:45.479 --> 20:48.916
SO, I'LL...

20:48.949 --> 20:50.417
MOVE MY SHIT IN.

20:50.450 --> 20:53.620
THE TWO OF YOU CAN STOP
DICKING AROUND ALREADY

20:53.654 --> 20:54.888
AND GET MARRIED,

20:54.922 --> 20:58.559
AND ON WE'LL GO...

20:58.592 --> 21:01.995
ONE BIG, HAPPY.

21:06.834 --> 21:11.004
Shane:
GET IN THE POOL, FAGS!

21:17.744 --> 21:19.847
[ FOOTSTEPS APPROACH ]

21:19.880 --> 21:23.016
YOU'RE EARLY.
I'M NOT EVEN DRESSED YET.

21:23.050 --> 21:26.019
WHAT'S THAT?

21:26.053 --> 21:28.856
WEDDING PRESENT.

21:28.889 --> 21:30.524
I FILLED OUT ALL THE FORMS

21:30.557 --> 21:33.193
TO PUT ESTEBAN'S NAME
ON THE BIRTH CERTIFICATE,

21:33.227 --> 21:35.696
SO SIGN THEM
AND WE'RE DONE.

21:35.729 --> 21:39.666
YOU DIDN'T MAKE A REGISTRY,
SO THIS WILL HAVE TO DO.

21:39.700 --> 21:42.503
I ACTUALLY DID MAKE
A REGISTRY ‐‐ WEEKS AGO.

21:42.536 --> 21:45.839
WILLIAMS‐SONOMA. WE COULD USE
A NEW TORTILLA WARMER.

21:45.873 --> 21:48.008
I'LL GET RIGHT ON THAT.

21:49.109 --> 21:50.777
ARE YOU SURE ABOUT THIS?

21:50.811 --> 21:53.113
YES.

21:54.882 --> 21:59.720
DO YOU HAVE, UM, A PLAN?

21:59.753 --> 22:02.022
I'M GONNA GO
BACK TO THE HOUSE

22:02.055 --> 22:04.925
AND SPREAD OUT MY LIFE
LIKE A MAP,

22:04.958 --> 22:07.561
DELIBERATE ON THE TOPOGRAPHY,
CHART MY PATH,

22:07.594 --> 22:11.498
MAYBE CALL A GIRL
WHO CALLS ME ON MY SHIT.

22:16.170 --> 22:21.508
YOU LOVE HIM.
YOU'RE GOING DOWN A ROAD.

22:24.211 --> 22:27.748
I‐I'M GOING DOWN A ROAD.

22:35.122 --> 22:37.791
I THINK I'M HAPPY FOR YOU.

22:37.824 --> 22:39.526
I THINK
I'M HAPPY FOR YOU, TOO.

22:42.829 --> 22:45.065
SEE YOU DOWNSTAIRS?

22:47.601 --> 22:50.437
[ CHUCKLES ]

22:53.640 --> 22:57.010
[ SIGHS ]

