23:59.706 --> 24:04.411
FOR THE NEXT...
15 MINUTES.

24:04.444 --> 24:07.481
WANT TO FUCK?

24:07.514 --> 24:09.149
YOU IN MY FUCK TRAILER.

24:09.183 --> 24:10.517
I JUST HAD A BABY,
YOU KNOW.

24:10.551 --> 24:12.753
IT'D BE LIKE THROWING
A HOT DOG DOWN A HALLWAY.

24:12.786 --> 24:14.054
[ CHUCKLES ]

24:14.087 --> 24:16.723
YOU GOT TO WORK
THOSE KEGELS.

24:16.757 --> 24:18.158
YOU KNOW, I GOT A COUSIN ‐‐

24:18.192 --> 24:21.061
SHE PRACTICED PUTTING PRESSURE
ON A CUCUMBER EVERY DAY.

24:21.094 --> 24:24.231
AND THEN SHE STOPPED
'CAUSE IT GOT STUCK IN THERE.

24:24.264 --> 24:26.900
AND THREE MONTHS LATER,
A PICKLE FELL OUT.

24:26.934 --> 24:28.468
I'LL HAVE TO TRY THAT.

24:28.502 --> 24:30.504
YOU KNOW, I COULD
FUCK YOU IN THE ASS.

24:30.537 --> 24:34.174
THAT'S TEMPTING.
BUT I'M NOT HERE TO SOCIALIZE.

24:34.208 --> 24:37.477
NO?
THEN WHY ARE YOU HERE?

24:37.511 --> 24:40.113
PILAR ZUAZO.

24:40.147 --> 24:43.617
I WANT HER DEAD.

